      <div class="table-responsive">
        <table class="change-password-table" id="noticeTable">
          <thead><tr><th>Date</th><th>Note</th></tr></thead>
          <tbody id="noticeTableBody">
            <tr data-notice-index="0"><td>25-07-25</td><td>Sub: Beginning of New Semester. Dear Parents. You are hereby informed that I. As per the university ordinance, it is mandatory to have 75% attendance. Student with less than 75 % attendance will be debarred from appearing in the upcoming university examination. 2. Students are required to register themselves with the department after deposition of fee only. Students without registration may be debarred from attending classes. 3. The last date for fee deposition without late fee is 20th July</td></tr>
            <tr data-notice-index="1"><td>09-07-24</td><td>Dear Students and Parents, Greeting from Maa Maturani Devi Pharmacy College Bhopal. For the new session, we kindly request that all outstanding fees be submitted before 20/07/2024. Please ensure that all fees are paid by the deadline to avoid any disruption.</td></tr>
            <tr data-notice-index="2"><td>26-06-24</td><td>Dear Students and Parents, Greeting from Maa Maturani Devi Pharmacy College Bhopal. This is to inform all Seventh Semester students that the new academic session will commence on 18/07/2023. In preparation for the new session, we kindly request that all outstanding fees be submitted before 20/07/2024. Important Dates: - New Session Starts: 18/07/2024 - Fee Submission Deadline: 20/07/2024 Please ensure that all fees are paid by the deadline to avoid any disruption in your</td></tr>
            <tr data-notice-index="3"><td>01-04-24</td><td>All students are instructed to visit this link for Mid Sem Time Table and view the time table <a href="https://www.nrigroupindia.com/niiit/mid-sem-timetable-on-01-04-24" target="_blank">https://www.nrigroupindia.com/niiit/mid-sem-timetable-on-01-04-24</a> It is mandatory for all students to enter the examination hall at 9:30 am.</td></tr>
            <tr data-notice-index="4"><td>14-03-24</td><td>All students are strictly instructed to not allowed in the campus 9:30am and exit time 3:00 pm</td></tr>
            <tr data-notice-index="5"><td>19-02-24</td><td>All the Students those who are going to be promoted in II & V Semester and MCA II Semester in academic Year 2024-25 are hereby informed that the session will be start from 19/02/2023 and the last date of Fee submission & Registration is 20th Jan 2024. The students must clear their dues before the declared date and the attendance minimum 75% as per university guidelines otherwise action will be taken against them as per the institute norms. As per the Guidelines of the regulating Authorities</td></tr>
            <tr data-notice-index="6"><td>19-02-24</td><td>Tuition fee and other fees in Cash Deposit in any case will not be entertained. The fee will only be accepted through online mode i.e through Students Registration ID (ERP). In case any assistance is required for online payment of fee, feel free to contact your Tutor Guardian/HOD or Mr. Neelesh</td></tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
